# 📝 MERN Blog Platform

A full-featured blog platform built using the MERN stack (MongoDB, Express.js, React, Node.js) with rich text editor, user authentication, admin dashboard, Cloudinary image uploads, and more.

## 🚀 Features

- 🧑‍💻 User Authentication (JWT-based)
- ✍️ Rich Text Blog Editor (React Quill)
- 🖼️ Cloudinary Image Upload
- 💬 Comments & Likes
- 🔐 Protected Routes
- 👮 Admin Dashboard
- 📦 MongoDB Atlas Integration
- 💡 Responsive UI with TailwindCSS

